    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('_buttons.ejs', {id: locals.id}) %>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="line-numbers">
                <h1 class="title"> ## Welcome to CodeHunt! </h1>
                <p><code>Sharing & storing your codes should be easy, but there isn't many options out there. What if I want to show you something I'm seeing or I'm working on? That's where we use pastebins or Haste. CodeHunt is easy to use and you are now able to store your code snippet in one location.</code>
                </p>
                <h1 class="title">## How to use Codehunt? </h1>
                <p><code>To make a new entry, click "New" on the top right</code></p>
                <h1 class="title"> ## My Code Snippets </h1>
                <p><code>↓your saved codes will be stored below↓</code></p>




                <% codehunts.forEach( codehunts=> { %>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <a href="/codehunt/<%=codehunts._id%>" class="savedCode">
                                <%=codehunts.name%>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                <% }) %>
            </div>
</body>

</html>